FAQ.question: What file formats do you support for transcription?
FAQ.answer: We support a wide range of audio and video formats including MP3, WAV, MP4, MOV, and many more. Our system can handle most common media formats.

FAQ.question: How accurate is the transcription?
FAQ.answer: Our AI-powered transcription service achieves high accuracy rates, typically above 95% for clear audio. The accuracy may vary depending on factors like audio quality, background noise, and speaker clarity.

FAQ.question: How long does it take to transcribe my file?
FAQ.answer: Our real-time transcription system processes files quickly. For most audio files, you'll receive your transcription within minutes. The exact time depends on the file length and complexity.
